Heya, thanks for getting to me. The spelling is intentional. First off the piece is set in the Coldest War. Anti-Russian sentiment is rising, and the Foundation has limited access to Russian translators.

Also, in the piece, the Russian translator was unable to properly translate the alternate reality Russian. It's a different type then ours, and they're understanding of both English and our Russian is skewed.







